1. Personal Use (Free)

  Individual users may use, copy, modify, and distribute this software
  free of charge for the following purposes:

  a) Personal learning, research, and experimentation;
  b) Personal non-commercial projects;
  c) Personal small-scale commercial projects with annual revenue
     not exceeding RMB 200,000 (or USD equivalent).

  All such use must retain this license in full along with the
  copyright notice.

2. Commercial Use (License Required)

  Prior written commercial authorization from the copyright holder
  is required in the following cases:

  a) Use by any enterprise, institution, or organization,
     whether for-profit or not;
  b) Use by individuals in commercial projects with annual revenue
     exceeding RMB 200,000;
  c) Offering this software as part of a SaaS, PaaS, or other
     online service to third parties;
  d) Embedding this software, in whole or in substantial part,
     into a commercial product for redistribution.

  For commercial licensing, contact: 505855752@qq.com

